text: Lourdes Hill College is a College of Good Samaritan Education in Brisbane with an enrolment of approximately 1250 girls. Applications are invited for 2 Senior English and Middle School English teaching positions. These are full-time contract positions commencing Tuesday 5 October and concluding on Friday 3 December. Applications close at 3.00pm on Friday 17 September, 2021. To view the position description please visit www. lhc. qld. edu. To Apply: Applications should be addressed to the Principal and submitted by email to lhc. qld. edu. Please include your current Curriculum Vitae, Cover Letter, and the names and contact details of at least two recent referees.
